| 🔴 High | No global error handler | Stack trace/info leakage |
| 🔴 High | No security headers | XSS, clickjacking, MIME sniffing |
| 🟠 Medium | No rate limiting | DoS / brute-force |
| 🟠 Medium | No 404 handler | Framework fingerprinting |
| 🟡 Low | No input validation | Future injection risk |
| 🟡 Low | Hardcoded port | Deployment inflexibility |

